'''格里姆赛岛'''（{{lang-is|Grímsey}}）位于[[冰岛|冰岛]]北部，[[格陵兰海|格陵兰海]]中，距冰岛主岛40公里，面积5.3平方公里，2011年1月拥有居民86人<ref>http://hagstofa.is/?PageID=2593&src=/temp/Dialog/varval.asp?ma=MAN03106%26ti=Mannfj%F6ldi+eftir+bygg%F0akj%F6rnum%2C+kyni+og+aldri+1%2E+jan%FAar+1998%2D2011+++++%26path=../Database/mannfjoldi/Byggdakjarnar/%26lang=3%26units=Fj%F6ldi {{Wayback|url=http://hagstofa.is/?PageID=2593&src=%2Ftemp%2FDialog%2Fvarval.asp%3Fma%3DMAN03106%26ti%3DMannfj%F6ldi+eftir+bygg%F0akj%F6rnum%2C+kyni+og+aldri+1.+jan%FAar+1998-2011+++++%26path%3D..%2FDatabase%2Fmannfjoldi%2FByggdakjarnar%2F%26lang%3D3%26units%3DFj%F6ldi |date=20200610122430 }}  Hagstofa Íslands; retrieved: 2011-11-25</ref>。格里姆赛岛是冰岛最北的居民点。[[北极圈|北极圈]]横穿岛北，是冰岛唯一位于北极圈内的领土。
